## Census Data

Raw block-group tabulations were downloaded from IPUMS NHGIS (https://www.nhgis.org).

Due to IPUMS redistribution terms, the raw NHGIS CSV extracts are not included in this repository. 
To replicate the analysis, download the following NHGIS extracts

- nhgis0013_ds120_1990_blck_grp.csv
- nhgis0013_ds147_2000_blck_grp.csv
- nhgis0013_ds172_2010_blck_grp.csv
- nhgis0013_ds248_2020_blck_grp.csv

The accompanying codebooks describe variable definitions and harmonization across decades.

`list1_2020.xls` provides the 2020 Core-Based Statistical Area (CBSA) delineations, mapping counties (FIPS State Code + FIPS County Code) to metropolitan areas.